text: Jessica Woynilko (born May 1, 1999) is an American professional wrestler and former gymnast. She is currently signed to WWE under the ring name Tiffany Stratton, where she performs on the SmackDown brand and is the current WWE Women's Champion in her first reign, and the winner of the 2024 Women's Money in the Bank ladder match.
